Package com.aevi.led

This package contains a helper class to control the LED on the aevi device.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LedPhase
    Defines a Phase for LED sequencing
    LedSequenceParams
    Defines settings for LED sequence params
    LedService
    The LedService provides control over the led on the Aevi device.
    LedServiceProvider
    The LedServiceProvider class gives an entry point to initialize a LedService

    After the LedServiceProvider is connected, by using the AeviServiceProvider.connect(com.aevi.helpers.services.AeviServiceConnectionCallback) function, a AeviServiceConnectionCallback is returned containing the initialized service.
